address2: Sheth Govindram Jolly Marg Kanjur Marg (East)
longBusinessSummary: NITCO Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the tiles and marble business in India and internationally. The company operates in two segments, Tiles and Related Products; and Real Estate segments. It offers glazed vitrified tiles; vitrified DCH, heavy duty, and SST tiles; wooden wall, floor, ceramic, and vitrifies tiles; ceramic wall and floor tiles; digital tiles; Italian tiles; and porcelain tiles, as well as marbles, mosaico tiles, and natural stone tiles. The company sells its products through under the Le Studio brand, Le Studio Express, and NITCO Look brands. It is also involved in the development of real estate properties. NITCO Limited was founded in 1953 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India.
